Additional notes:

This project is maintained by someone with hands-on experience flashing and
running the ROMs, recoveries, and tools it indexes. Contributions from people
who have not read the codebase and do not have direct experience with Android
modding will not be accepted.

Pull requests from non-collaborators will be closed. If you want to contribute,
reach out first. Do not show up with code nobody asked for.

Forks for personal study are fine. Publishing a fork as a replacement for this
project is not.

Data shown by Droidify (ROM builds, device specs, tool versions, recovery files)
belongs to the respective upstream projects. Droidify does not host any files.
All download links point to official upstream servers.

Flashing your device is your responsibility. The author is not liable for
bricked devices, tripped Knox fuses, or voided warranties.
